::Prowl::

Prowl turns around in his seat. Also hearing the gunfire, he pushes several 
buttons on the controll panel and the screen brings up a visual of the area, 
just in time to short out as the grenade explodes.

Prowl swears, jumping out of his seat and pulling out his acid gun.

"Get everyone seated," he says calmly to Sniper and runs off toward the 
explosion.
